# fxmanifest.lua standards

- Always use `fx_version 'cerulean'` (the current and only supported version)
- Always specify `games { 'gta5' }` or `games { 'rdr3' }` or both
- Never use the deprecated `__resource.lua` format
- Include `author`, `description`, and `version` metadata
- Use glob patterns for script includes: `client_scripts { 'client/*.lua' }`
- Declare all dependencies explicitly with `dependency`
- Do not use `lua54 'yes'` -- it is deprecated and ignored since Lua 5.3 was removed. All scripts run on Lua 5.4 automatically.
- List NUI files under `files {}` and set `ui_page` for NUI resources
- Order: fx_version, games, metadata, dependencies, scripts, files, ui_page
